Eh, shaddap! Prowl's very airodinamic :-)

::Prowl::

Prowl sees that he indeed wasn't gaining on this diving bot, it was
just the lack of knowledge of the person that was writing his posts
that was making him think he was. He hears the command from Halucigen.
The control bug was beginning to wear off, but it still had some
effect.

Prowl lands on the ground, seeing Iron Raptor walking toward
Fireblade. He tilts his head. The beast side of him was curious in
seeing another beast like it, as they wern't common at all. Forgetting
about his 'orders', he walks off toward Iron Raptor, reaching her and
sniffing at her privates, much like a dog does to get to know another
dog.
